dct_title_s: Carte de voies de communication du Brésil
dct_description_sm: At head of title: Estados Unidos do Brazil. Shows railroad and steamship routes. Text in French on verso with title: Le Brésil. With data tables on trains, current and under construction. Inset map of North and South America, Europe and Africa showing steamship routes.
dct_publisher_sm: Paris : la Mission de Propagande et d'Expansion Économique, 1908.
